                "width": 0.17884130982367757,
                "height": 0.17042755344418054,
                "page": 3,
                "original_page": 3
              },
              "content": "由 \\( 5 a+6 b=10 \\Rightarrow b=\\frac{10-5 a}{6} \\) 。\n\\( a b=a \\cdot \\frac{10-5 a}{6}=\\frac{10 a-5 a^{2}}{6} \\)\n為一開口向下的二次函數。最大值在\n\\( a=-\\frac{b}{2 a}=-\\frac{10}{2 \\times(-5)}=1 \\)\n代入 \\( a=1 \\) 得 \\( b=\\frac{10-5}{6}=\\frac{5}{6} \\) 。\n\\( a b=\\frac{1 \\times 5}{6}=\\frac{5}{6} \\)\n答案：最大值 \\( =\\frac{5}{6} \\)",
              "image_url": null,
              "confidence": "high",
              "granular_confidence": {
                "extract_confidence": null,
                "parse_confidence": 0.8887030839920044
