              "content": "解：\n對 \\( x \\) 取導數：\n\\( f^{\\prime}(x)=\\frac{1}{12}-\\frac{75}{x^{2}}=0 \\Rightarrow x^{2}=900 \\Rightarrow x=30 \\)",
